collectionMetadata.name: Number of Active CPF Members by Regrossed Balances as at end of Year
collectionMetadata.description:
An active CPF member refers to a person who has at least 1 CPF employment contribution paid for him for the current or any of the preceding 3 months.
Regrossed balances include amounts withdrawn under Investment, Education, Residential Properties, Non-Residential Properties and Public Housing Schemes as at end of year.
Figures on number of active CPF members exclude all self-employed persons, and are rounded to the nearest ten.
Figures on regrossed balances are rounded to the nearest thousand dollars.
